# Results Summary

## Prototype Testing

The prototype successfully demonstrated basic seismic signal acquisition, preprocessing, and machine learning classification.

---

## Current Features

- Real-time signal acquisition
- CSV data logging
- Statistical feature extraction
- FFT analysis
- Basic machine learning classification
- Early warning simulation

---

## Observations

- Noise signals showed lower amplitude variation.
- Simulated P-wave-like signals produced earlier detectable patterns.
- Simulated S-wave-like signals showed larger amplitude activity.

